entries.s_32: The Emperor sent you? I understand his wishes. But first you need to retrieve a datadisk from a Rebel base on Dantooine. Return after you have it and after it has been altered by an Imperial operative in Kaadara.
entries.s_34: What are you doing in here? Security!
entries.s_5: You have the disk? Good. Let the Emperor know that I am prepared to do his bidding.
